  "description": "**Milestone:** Phase 2: Component Expansion\n\nBuild hx-icon: SVG icon system with sprite support. Load sprite via Drupal libraries.yml; reference by name. Supports inline SVG and external sprite references.\n\n**Files to Modify:**\n- packages/hx-library/src/components/hx-icon/\n\n**Acceptance Criteria:**\n- [ ] Inline SVG and external sprite reference modes\n- [ ] Configurable sprite URL\n- [ ] Sizes: xs, sm, md, lg, xl\n- [ ] Color inherits from currentColor\n- [ ] CSS parts: svg\n- [ ] Lazy loading for external sprites\n- [ ] ARIA: role=img with aria-label, or aria-hidden for decorative\n- [ ] <5KB gzipped\n\n**Complexity:** medium",
